  <brief_title>A Trial Using Velcade Plus Chemoradiation for Central Nervous System, Head and Neck, and Cervical Cancer Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase I Open-labeled, Dose-escalation, Safety Study of the Combination of Velcade and Chemoradiation for the Treatment of Cancer Patients</official_title>
